result.name: Tsui Wah Restaurant

reviews.text: Food quality and service are both deteriorating. But some branches in less prime locations are quite easy to find a table thanks for this shortcoming and quite trully HK resturant style allowing schatting for a long time
Price raise 20% in silent.  That's why you can always find free seats.

Not all Tsui Wah branches can offer you a good time because they are always busy. This particular branch is a bit different because it's in a residential area. The food and service are generally better. TW is known for milktea. For those who like strong tea flavored milktea, you will probably enjoy both hot and cold ones there.

Large chain of HK style café, but it feels like they are trying to do too many things with none of them being very good. Had the fried instant noodles with pork chop on hot plate which was decent. Liked that there was chili sauce and mustard served with the dish. The almond milk had egg white in it, would have preferred it on it's own.

Tried the fish fillet, burnt my tongue due to the heat. Waitress's finger nails were dirty, tables were semi dirty too. Food is okay, nice interior, calm and peaceful. Staff can't manage to speak English, even on basic level. But they were friendly. All in all not bad, but not excellent.

result.name: 翠華餐廳

reviews.text: 以香港一般餐廳小而擠來說，座位坐起來算舒服，空間不會太擁擠，食物也還不錯。
帶一群外國朋友來吃晚餐，服務生們都很友善熱情，環境乾淨，是很棒的體驗！
真的很油。用餐只推薦蝦撈麵，凍檸茶不加蜂蜜。
食物質素飄忽不定多數都係差嘅，員工態度亦非常一般
呢間很好，乾淨，闊落
